title: Trumble-Rettke Engagement
maintext:
The parents of Kristie Trumble and Lucas Rettke, both of Kankakee, are happy to announce the engagement and approaching marriage of their children. The couple will be married April 13 at Hudson Farm in Urbana, with the reception to follow.
Kristie is the daughter of David and Janice Trumble, of Crescent City. Lucas is the son of Dennis and Amy Rettke, of Limestone.
